# Tender Notification

**Tender Title:** Linear Hydraulic/Pneumatic Actuators

**Reference Number:** PW-22-01012371
**Solicitation Number:** W8482-230972/A
**Publication Date:** November 3, 2022
**Tender Closing Date:** December 13, 2022, 14:00:00 (Local Time)
**
#### Solicitation Overview

The Department of National Defence is seeking to acquire Linear Hydraulic/Pneumatic Actuators through a competitive Request for Proposal (RFP) process.

**Procurement Details**

* Estimated quantity: 40
* Duration of contract: April 1, 2023, to March 31, 2024
* Time frame of delivery: April 1, 2023, to March 31, 2024

#### Contract Requirements

The RFP is seeking bids for the delivery of Linear Hydraulic/Pneumatic Actuators at CFB Esquimalt and CFB Halifax. The items to be procured are:

* GSIN: 4810, NSN: 21-910-9680, Part No.: 700784-026-999, NCAGE: 81576, Unit of Issue: EA, Quantity: 20

Bidders proposing an equivalent or substitute product must indicate the brand name and model, Part Number, and NCAGE. All bids must be submitted in Canadian dollars; foreign currency bids will be rejected.

#### Notice of Proposed Procurement

The Department of National Defence requires the items detailed below:

* CFB Esquimalt: 20 EA of Linear Hydraulic/Pneumatic Actuators, GSIN: 4810, NSN: 21-910-9680, Part No.: 700784-026-999, NCAGE: 81576
* CFB Halifax: 20 EA of Linear Hydraulic/Pneumatic Actuators, GSIN: 4810, NSN: 21-910-9680, Part No.: 700784-026-999, NCAGE: 81576

The tender documentation is available in both official languages of Canada. Suppliers interested in participating must submit a proposal, including all necessary documentation and prices in Canadian dollars.

#### Contact Information

For further information, please contact:

* Names: Normandin, Jean-Pierre
* Email: jean-pierre.normandin@forces.gc.ca
* Telephone: 819-939-3674
